    entrepreneursService1DetailText1: "We have more than 10 years of experience with digital accounting and have been using DATEV Company Online for 4 years.",
    entrepreneursService1DetailText2: "The tax office requires clean and timely financial management. Using digital solutions, we make accounting as uncomplicated as possible for you too. The magic words here are digital receipt transfer and electronic retrieval of account transactions.",
    entrepreneursService1DetailText3: "You can comfortably record receipts digitally in your company and then transmit them directly to us online. In addition, there is the 'DATEV Upload mobile' app, with which you can digitally record receipts such as cash receipts directly with your smartphone while on the go. Receipts are recorded upon receipt and no longer need to be sorted laboriously. This brings significant time savings in preparing the accounting!",
    entrepreneursService1DetailText4: "Electronic retrieval of account transactions and receipt transfer enable us to provide timely accounting where you always have your receivables and liabilities exactly in view.",
    entrepreneursService1DetailSubtitle: "In addition to posting your receipts, we offer you the following services:",
