    entrepreneursService2DetailText2: "You can upload all relevant documents, such as personnel questionnaires, employee timesheets, vacation days, sick leave certificates, etc., directly into the digital personnel file and no longer need to keep separate lists in view. Changes to master data and recording new employees in the company can also be easily done in Company Online.",
    entrepreneursService2DetailText3: "After data processing, you receive payroll evaluations immediately digitally in Company Online and can view them anywhere and anytime.",
    entrepreneursService2DetailText4: "Some comfortable automations are also possible. On request, we can make payments for social security contributions and wages/salaries directly from the system. For this, a transfer form is created for your house bank and submitted there. After successful processing, you can release the payroll payment and your house bank then executes it as a bulk transfer. Individual transfers are thus eliminated for you.",
    entrepreneursService2DetailText5: "In addition, all transmitted data is digitally stored in the DATEV data center and thus securely archived. If needed, these documents can be quickly reproduced for you and your employees.",
    entrepreneursService2DetailText6: "For your employees, there is the 'Employee Online' module. Through this, your employees can retrieve their own payroll documents online. This saves paper and time.",
