    entrepreneursService3DetailText1: "After 12 months, a line is drawn under the business year: a transparent and clean annual financial statement is required. Several addressee groups are usually interested in an annual financial statement. The publication of the annual financial statement itself and the manner in which it is done are also dependent on legal form and size. In some cases, only a balance sheet must be filed.",
    entrepreneursService3DetailText2: "In addition to the required submission to the tax office and publication with the Federal Office of Justice, the annual financial statement and balance sheet primarily serve as a control element for your company's success. The annual financial statement and balance sheet provide insights into the development of your company in the past and thus also impulses for future entrepreneurial activities and targeted decisions.",
    entrepreneursService3DetailText3: "We look at what requirements are placed on your company. Through our years of experience, we not only prepare your financial statement, but also advise you individually on promising measures for the future.",
